query:
SELECT 
  id,
  propertyId,
  buyerName,
  saleType,
  contractPrice,
  downPayment,
  installmentAmount,
  installmentCount,
  contractDate,
  firstInstallmentDate,
  balloonAmount,
  balloonDate,
  status
FROM contracts
WHERE saleType = 'CFD' AND status = 'Active'
ORDER BY propertyId;
